Name: Group Pose
Description: Perform a group pose, repeating the last executed emote or action on loop. Camera position, lighting, and color filter can be all be adjusted in the command settings. Text Command: /grouppose Key Mapping: Available

Name: Idling Camera
Description: Enable the idling camera. While active, the idling camera will randomly toggle between nearby PCs and NPCs. Executing the command with a PC or NPC targeted will center the camera on that target. Camera position, lighting, and color filter can be all be adjusted in the command settings. Text Command: /idlingcamera Key Mapping: Available

Name: Alarm
Description: Enable alarm. Alarms can be set to go off while in game and are deleted upon logout. Text Command: /alarm Key Mapping: Available
